title: Oneechanbara
description:
The famed b-movie originating from the game Oneechanbara (Or Zombie Hunters here in the Western world) 

It adds up backstory for the characters, but really its all about the zombie battles isnt it? I have to say I waited a long time (From since I heard about the theatrical release) and I got even more giddy when I heard it was being shown on that special asian week in the US. But day in and out I waited and I never got my lovely Oneechanbara. And all of a sudden I spot it on a forum divided up in a bunch of rapidshare links. So strugglingly without a rapidshare account I downloaded it. And hell, this is a quite goody quality with English subtitles release.

With it I am including the poster and the trailer. The subtitles are hardcoded into the video, so I cant do anything about that.

I just hope you&#039;ll enjoy it. I did :)
